and missed barcodes (recall) for linear barcodes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Some barcode types are naturally prone to false positives (e.g. MSI Plessey)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For those barcode types false positives can be drastically reduced (precision can be increased) by requiring that multiple scan-lines in the input scan to the same result."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode","title":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.1","type":"text"}],"title":"ScanbotSDK","type":"topic","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk","kind":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotSDK/documentation/ScanbotSDK/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode/thorough":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationModeThorough","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotsdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode\/thorough","abstract":[{"text":"Recommended. Thorough confirmation is performed. Almost completely eliminates false positives, at the cost of an additional slight decrease in recall.","type":"text"}],"title":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode.thorough","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"thorough","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotSDK\/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode\/thorough","type":"topic"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","value":"occ","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadat